snippet.title: Quake Maps - Brightfolds
snippet.description:
Custom Quake Map: Brightfolds
Author: Pinchy
Year: 2020

Download: https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/dtintin_fixed.html

This is Pinchy's submission to the Doom Tintin Jam.

This video uses the updated "Alternate Quake Music" pack, to avoid
copyright claim garbage. You can get it here: http://www.quaketastic.com/files/music/aqm2_pack.zip
